    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels brand new? I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it is in stunning shape! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, and the interior is still smelling fresh. I've truly babied this car, and I'd love to see it go to someone who will appreciate it just as much as I have. Come take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
