    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen boasts documented subframe reinforcement and preventative rod bearing replacement, ensuring structural and internal longevity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with mechanical precision, paired with a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential. Every bushing, damper, and seal remains in peak operational condition, offering the tactile feedback and linear power delivery these chassis are celebrated for. Garage-kept with a flawless finish, this is a turn-key example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
