    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-grade vehicle that satisfies even the most rigorous inspection. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in an exterior finish that is entirely free of rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. The paint retains its original deep luster, enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear or bolster compression, and the interior still carries a faint factory-new scent. Every switch, dial, and digital display functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. It delivers a driving experience that is tight, responsive, and indistinguishable from its original delivery state. This sale includes all original owner's manuals, two sets of master keys, and the original window sticker. For the discerning buyer seeking a collector-quality example, this is an unparalleled opportunity.",
      "price": 45500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
