      "description": "We are honored to present this superlative vehicle, a specimen that reflects an extraordinary level of preservation and mechanical stewardship. Every aspect of this automobile\u2014from its flawless exterior finish to its pristine, factory-fresh interior\u2014adheres to the highest standards of excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained, ensuring it remains in showroom condition for the most discerning of buyers. This offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a premier example of automotive engineering in unrivaled condition.",
      "price": 44900.0,
