    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem! It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is in truly spectacular shape\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a single scratch or dent, and the interior is still smelling brand new. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. You won't find another one this clean! Come take a look, you're going to fall in love!",
      "price": 43500.0,
